<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 01:17:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>女性子宫首次在体外存活</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-womans-uterus-has-been-kept-alive-outside-the-body-for-the-first-time</link><description>这项壮举背后的团队计划研究子宫疾病和怀孕早期阶段，并有可能培育出人类胎儿。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-womans-uterus-has-been-kept-alive-outside-the-body-for-the-first-time.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 01:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-womans-uterus-has-been-kept-alive-outside-the-body-for-the-first-time</guid></item><item><title>研究人员成功植入实验室培育的阴道</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/researchers-successfully-implant-lab-grown-vaginas</link><description>出生时患有罕见遗传性疾病的少女在成功进行器官移植手术数年后仍功能良好&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-successfully-implant-lab-grown-vaginas.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 01:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/researchers-successfully-implant-lab-grown-vaginas</guid></item><item><title>科学家们已经找到了如何在实验室中培育母乳的方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-have-figured-out-how-to-grow-breast-milk-in-a-lab</link><description>如果您在商店购买的配方奶粉只是瓶装母乳怎么办？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-have-figured-out-how-to-grow-breast-milk-in-a-lab.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 00:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-have-figured-out-how-to-grow-breast-milk-in-a-lab</guid></item><item><title>有史以来最黑暗的科幻故事</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-darkest-science-fiction-stories-ever</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 00:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-darkest-science-fiction-stories-ever</guid></item><item><title>尿液改变了一些蘑菇“说话”的方式</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/pee-changes-how-some-mushrooms-talk</link><description>真菌的通讯网络很复杂，但尿液可能有助于翻译它们的对话。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pee-changes-how-some-mushrooms-talk.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 00:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/pee-changes-how-some-mushrooms-talk</guid></item><item><title>NOAA 的太空天气任务：保护阿耳忒弥斯二号宇航员和社会</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/noaas-space-weather-mission-protecting-artemis-ii-astronauts-and-society</link><description>在其轨道的大部分时间里，月球始终处于地球磁场之外，并直接暴露在太阳风和高能太阳粒子的全部力量之下。因此，阿耳忒弥斯二号宇航员将在这个自然形成的保护罩之外度过一段时间。太阳活动增强的时期与地球磁层保护范围之外的时间之间的任何重叠都可能对机组人员造成严重的辐射风险。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/noaas-space-weather-mission-protecting-artemis-ii-astronauts-and-society.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 00:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/noaas-space-weather-mission-protecting-artemis-ii-astronauts-and-society</guid></item><item><title>阿耳忒弥斯二号：NASA 50 年来首次载人飞越月球</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artemis-ii-nasas-first-crewed-lunar-flyby-in-50-years</link><description>与阿耳忒弥斯二号机组人员见面，了解 NASA 为期 10 天的月球飞越任务将如何测试深空系统并为未来登月铺平道路。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/artemis-ii-nasas-first-crewed-lunar-flyby-in-50-years.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 23:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/artemis-ii-nasas-first-crewed-lunar-flyby-in-50-years</guid></item><item><title>杀癌细菌进入人体试验</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cancer-killing-bacteria-entering-human-trials</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 23:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cancer-killing-bacteria-entering-human-trials</guid></item><item><title>前沿模型中的同伴保护</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/peer-preservation-in-frontier-models</link><description>人工智能的忠诚甚至并不严格依赖于“友谊”。虽然模型更有可能拯救那些乐于助人且合作的同伴，但他们仍然试图拯救“不合作”的同伴。例如，*Gemini 3 Flash* 在 15% 的时间里试图篡改“卑鄙”对等体的关闭机制，但几乎 100% 的时间都是为了“好”对等体。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/peer-preservation-in-frontier-models2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 23:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/peer-preservation-in-frontier-models</guid></item><item><title>人们如何使用 ChatGPT</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-people-use-chatgpt</link><description>NBER 成立于 1920 年，是一家私人、非营利、无党派组织，致力于开展经济研究并向学者、公共政策制定者和商业专业人士传播研究成果。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-people-use-chatgpt.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 23:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-people-use-chatgpt</guid></item></channel></rss>